title: A&M Part II: Lani Hall / Baja Marimba Band
description:
Lani Hall:
1) Sun Down Lady
2) Sweet Bird
3) Hello It's Me
4) Double or Nothing

I included only her first four becuase these have Herb Alpert at the production helm.  Albums 2-4 I dubbed from vinyl myself, #1 I found online.

Baja Marimba Band:
1) Do You Know the Way to San Jose?
2) Fowl Play
3) Fresh Air
4) Heads Up!
5) The Baja Marimba Band Rides Again
6) Those Were the Days
7) Watch Out!

I desperately wanted to include the self titled debut and 'For Animals Only' but I've had a hell of a time finding them and I dont feel like buying the vinyl as my collection is already out of control and now I have no reason to get the rest of the discography.  If anyone has access to either album, I'd appreciate letting me know!

Comment -- Seed -- ENJOY!
